T:L^{2}(\mathbf{T}) \longrightarrow l^2(\mathbf{Z})
T(f) =(f^{\wedge}(n))_{n \in \mathbf{z}}
\forall f,g \in L^2(T)
\left<f,g\right>_{L^2(\mathbf{T})}=\left<f ^\wedge,g^\wedge\right>_{l^2(\mathbf{Z})}
f^\wedge=(f^{\wedge}(n))_{n \in \mathbf{z}}
g^\wedge=(g^{\wedge}(n))_{n \in \mathbf{z}}
\langle f+g,f+g \rangle
\langle f+ig,f+ig \rangle
